#CHATS INDEX
the chatroom index should list the user's chatrooms

the chatroom index should not list chatrooms to which the user does not belong

clicking on the chatroom should go to that specific chatroom

#CHATS NEW
User should be able to create new chat by typing valid username

User should be able to create new group chat by typing valid usernames

User should be able to create new chat by typing valid phone number

User should be able to create new group chat by typing valid phone numbers

User should be able to create new group chat by typing valid phone number and username

User should receive 'no user found error' if no valid username found

User should receive 'no user found error' if no valid phone number found


